metadata.name: Simeji #1
metadata.description: Simeji is favored by trend-sensitive Gen-Z users and is leading the change of trends in Japan. Our users are life enthusiasts who possess humor and positivity. Let's create trends, choose your favorite skin, and use trendy emojis and Memes! We can only go further with the support of our users. We want to create the "next trend" with everyone who is a part of our community. The core driving force behind Simeji's determination to enter Web3 is to give backto every contributor and supporter of our lovely Simeji Community. Ready to join the Web3 era with us?
